data.description: Gorgeous home nestled in Lake Cove, a premium Seabrook community!  Beautifully updated chef’s kitchen with an island, double ovens, a gas cooktop and room for more than one chef!  Counter and cabinet space abound!  Elegant & stylish tile flooring adorns the kitchen & family room.  Expansive family room includes a gas log fireplace.  Spacious primary bedroom downstairs with a raised ceiling, his-n-hers walkin closets, ensuite bath w/double sink vanities. Super-sized game room along with three generously bedrooms, large walkin closets & a storage room accent the second story.  Relax in your backyard oasis with a covered patio/deck, sparkling pool w/waterfall, outdoor kitchen & play area.  NO BACK NEIGHBORS, just beautiful trees!  Desirable subdivision amenities include a community boat ramp, neighborhood park, pool & tennis.  Easy access to Highway 99/Grand Parkway.  Just minutes to nearby destinations & attractions in Kemah, NASA and Galveston. Zoned to Clear Creek School District.
